        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/william_kelley/{size}/2314_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-02-13T13:22:32.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"149933\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Does anyone have intelligence on the release of the 2015 or 2016 vintages of 3.14 for the US market? Has Kermit Lynch not distributed them? CellarTracker shows hundreds of bottles of the 2014 in cellars, but only 4 pending bottles of the 2015 and no bottles of the 2016. If I recall, the 2014 was available in the US market as of mid- to late 2016. So it seems like there has been a change of schedule for recent vintages.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>And I don\u2019t think they made one in 2016 what with the hail that hit Morgon.</p>",
